## DEPENDENCIES

Uses CMake to manage build files, dependencies and such.
CMake creates Makefile(s) that work with GNU make.
The file src/CMakeLists.txt configures CMake.

Compiles with clang, gcc and most modern compilers.

## BUILDING

	$ mkdir -p bin
	$ cd bin
	$ cmake ../src
	$ make clean
	$ make

